**Steps to Reproduce**:

```csharp
#nullable enable

using System.Diagnostics.CodeAnalysis;

public class Base<T>
{
	[return: MaybeNull]
	public virtual T M() => default;
}

public class Derived : Base<object>
{
	public override object? M() => default;
}
```

**Expected Behavior**: No Diagnostic

**Actual Behavior**: CS8609: Nullability of reference types in return type doesn't match overridden member.

